This is a personal project, to be developed on my free time to help me understand and evolve
my solidity and EVM knowledge. 

I decided to play with this after reading Vitaliks Transitions blog post.

Feel free to do whatever u want with the code or contribute to what's here. 

ZkPrivacyHub is a novel privacy-preserving architecture for Ethereum Layer 2 solutions, 
leveraging zk-SNARKs to facilitate private transactions. This library aims to create a 
seamless integration of privacy-focused techniques with smart contract wallets, to enable 
a new paradigm of blockchain interaction that prioritizes user anonymity and data protection.